comments.content:
I don't see "MissingRequiredOptions: Auth plugin requires parameters which were not given: auth_url" in your log dump above. But it looks like you don't have something configured correctly to make requests to keystone. Double check your keystone and service catalog (endpoint/service) setup and configuration files. But this isn't really a bug, it's a support request. You might try the ask.openstack.org forum, general openstack mailing list:

https://wiki.openstack.org/wiki/Mailing_Lists#General_List

Or #openstack channel in freenode IRC.
